  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        To meet participant eligibility criteria, individuals must be 18 years of age or older
        (adult intervention) or between 10-17 years of age (youth intervention), a resident of the
        Flint or greater Flint community, and English speaking.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        We will attempt to exclude those who cannot read English because they will not be able to
        benefit from the intervention materials. These criteria will be confirmed during
        assessment procedures prior to enrollment.
      </textblock>
